snippet.title: Tony and Friends in Kellogg Land gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Tony and Friends in Kellogg Land, Dos PC game produced by Kellogg Company in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/tony-and-friends-in-kellogg-land/6152/
Playing the game in its german language version. It's a platform game made from Kellogs company to advertise its products.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
